  "description": "Implement About Page Navigation Link\n\nUpdate the \"Dowiedz się więcej\" (Learn More) button on the homepage to correctly navigate to the about page with proper language routing.\n\nRequirements:\n- Locate the \"Dowiedz się więcej\" link/button element on the homepage\n- Update the href/navigation target to route to `/<lang>/about/` where `<lang>` is the current language context\n- Ensure the language parameter dynamically reflects the user's active language (e.g., `/en/about/`, `/pl/about/`, etc.)\n- Verify the link works correctly for all supported languages\n- Test that the about page exists at the target route and renders properly\n- Ensure proper routing behavior (no 404 errors, correct page loads)\n- Maintain existing styling and behavior of the button",
